title: Final Exam
details: In this course, we will use MongoDB, which is a document database designed for ease of development and scaling. The reason we choose this database is because it is easy to learn for people who use JavaScript. Even if you have never used a database or you do not know how to write SQL queries, you should be able to learn MongDB fairly quickly.
